meta {
  name: Agent - Order Status
  type: http
  seq: 7
}

post {
  url: {{ai_url}}/agent
  body: json
  auth: none
}

body:json {
  {
    "message": "What is the status of order {{order_id}}?",
    "userId": "{{customer_id}}"
  }
}

docs {
  ## Agent — Order Status

  Triggers the `GetOrderStatusTool` inside the agent.
  The agent extracts the order GUID from the message, calls `GET /order/{id}`, and returns the current status.

  ### When is this tool triggered?
  The message must contain **order / order status / track order** AND a valid UUID.

  ### Response
  ```json
  {
    "answer": "Your order abc-123 is currently Processing. Total: $99.00, placed on 2026-01-15.",
    "usedTools": true
  }
  ```

  > If the order ID is not found, `usedTools` is `false` and the LLM replies generically.
}
